quran[27]{c,v,t}:
  68,16,Senesimuhu ÂṀalelhurtumi
  68,17,ÄḞnna belevnahum kema belevna ashabelcenneti iz aksemu leyasri munneha musbihÄḟyne
  68,18,Ve la yestesnune
  68,19,Fetafe ÂṀaleyha taifun min rabbike ve hum naimune
  68,20,Feasbehat kessariymi
  68,21,Fetenadev musbihÄḟyne
