  68,28,Kale evsetuhum elem ekul lekum levha tusebbihune
  68,29,Kalu subhane rabbina inna kunna zalimiyne
  68,30,Feakbele baÂṀduhum ÂṀala baÂṀdÄḟn yetelavemune
  68,31,Kalu ya veylena inna kunna taÄÄḟyne
  68,32,ÂṀasa rabbuna en yubdilena hayren minha inna ila rabbina raÄÄḟbune
  68,33,KezalikelÂṀazabu ve leÂṀazabulÂṀahÄḟreti ekberu lev kanu yaÂṀlemune
  68,34,ÄḞnne lilmuttekÄḟyne ÂṀÄḟnde rabbihim cennatin neÂṀÄḟymi
  68,35,EfenecÂṀalulmuslimiyne kelmucrimiyne
  68,36,Ma lekum keyfe tahkumune
  68,37,Emlekum kitabun fiyhi tedrusune
  68,38,ÄḞnne lekum fiyhu lema tehayyerune
  68,39,Em lekum eymanun ÂṀaleyna baliÄatun ila yevmilkÄḟyameti inne lekum lema tahkumune
  68,40,Selhum eyyuhum bizalike zeÂṀÄḟymun
  68,41,Emlehum ÅurekaÂṀu felyeÂṀtu biÅurekaihim in kanu sadikÄḟyne
  68,42,Yevme yukÅefu ÂṀan sakÄḟn ve yudÂṀavne ilessucudi fela yestetÄḟyÂṀune